      <title>鲍勃·梅嫩德斯 (Bob Menendez) 贿赂案审判移至 5 月 13 日，律师仍在审理此案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bob-menendez-bribe-trial-moved-to-may-13-as-lawyer-stays-on-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅内德斯及两名商人的受贿案审判被推迟一周至 5 月 13 日，法官称，该案已就一份声明进行了谈判，以避免取消同案被告的律师资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bob-menendez-bribe-trial-moved-to-may-13-as-lawyer-stays-on-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 16:53:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
