      <title>众议院在民主党的帮助下推进乌克兰援助和 TikTok 禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/house-advances-ukraine-aid-tik-tok-ban-with-democrats-help</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院推进了一项长期搁置的针对乌克兰、以色列和台湾的 950 亿美元援助计划，这一突破标志着乌克兰和美国在欧洲盟友日益痛苦的等待结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/house-advances-ukraine-aid-tik-tok-ban-with-democrats-help</guid>
